      "writtenOn": "2018-02-28T16:51:55Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "We can omit that and add it later if needed. \n\ntotalImg \u003d # of all images created by the tryjobs. \nnewImg \u003d # of previously unseen images. \nuntriageImg \u003d # of images that have not been triaged \n\nThis is always true: untriagedImg \u003c\u003d newImg \u003c\u003d totalImg \n\nIt covers the use case of iterating and triaging as results come in. \nIn the case of a project that wants to triage everything before a CL lands \nthat means untriageImg should be 0 after all bots have run.",
